<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="holiday-n">holiday <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hɒlədeɪ,'hɒlədi/    美 /'hɑːlədeɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 假日；节日：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a national holiday
全国性的假日</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u-ame-vacation">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 假期 (AmE vacation)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have / take a holiday</strong>
休假</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Have you decided where to go <strong>for your holiday</strong>?
你决定去哪里度假了吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She usually <strong>goes on holiday</strong> in the summer.
她通常夏天时出去度假。</p><footer>译林② – 2</footer></div></div>